# Frontend Environment Variables for AstroBuild List

# API Configuration
# For development, use local backend
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:3001/api

# Environment
NODE_ENV=development

# Development Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file to .env.local
# 2. Update NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL if your backend runs on a different port
# 3. Run 'npm run dev' to start development server

# Production Instructions:
# 1. Update .env.production with your actual backend URL
# 2. Deploy to Vercel using 'vercel' command or GitHub integration
# 3. Vercel will automatically use .env.production for production builds